    • Field Detail

      • PATH

        static final BitField PATH
        This flag is meaningful in EmfPlusPathGradientBrushData objects. If set, an EmfPlusBoundaryPathData object MUST be specified in the BoundaryData field of the brush data object. If clear, an EmfPlusBoundaryPointData object MUST be specified in the BoundaryData field of the brush data object.(此标志在EmfPlusPathJournentBrushData对象中有意义。如果已设置，则必须在画笔数据对象的BoundaryData字段中指定EmfPlusBoundaryPathData对象。如果清除，则必须在画笔数据对象的BoundaryData字段中指定EmfPlusBoundaryPointData对象。)

      • TRANSFORM

        static final BitField TRANSFORM
        This flag is meaningful in EmfPlusLinearGradientBrushData objects , EmfPlusPathGradientBrushData objects, and EmfPlusTextureBrushData objects. If set, a 2x3 world space to device space transform matrix MUST be specified in the OptionalData field of the brush data object.(该标志在EmfPlusLinearEnsementBrushData对象、EmfPlusPathEnsementBrushData对象和EmfPlusTextureBrushData对象中有意义。如果设置，则必须在画笔数据对象的OptionalData字段中指定2x 3世界空间到设备空间的转换矩阵。)

      • PRESET_COLORS

        static final BitField PRESET_COLORS
        This flag is meaningful in EmfPlusLinearGradientBrushData and EmfPlusPathGradientBrushData objects. If set, an EmfPlusBlendColors object MUST be specified in the OptionalData field of the brush data object.(此标志在EmfPlusLinearEnsementBrushData和EmfPlusPathEnsementBrushData对象中有意义。如果已设置，则必须在画笔数据对象的OptionalData字段中指定EmfPlusBlendColors对象。)

      • BLEND_FACTORS_H

        static final BitField BLEND_FACTORS_H
        This flag is meaningful in EmfPlusLinearGradientBrushData and EmfPlusPathGradientBrushData objects. If set, an EmfPlusBlendFactors object that specifies a blend pattern along a horizontal gradient MUST be specified in the OptionalData field of the brush data object.(此标志在EmfPlusLinearEnsementBrushData和EmfPlusPathEnsementBrushData对象中有意义。如果已设置，则必须在画笔数据对象的OptionalData字段中指定指定沿着水平渐变的混合图案的EmfPlusBlendFactors对象。)

      • BLEND_FACTORS_V

        static final BitField BLEND_FACTORS_V
        This flag is meaningful in EmfPlusLinearGradientBrushData objects. If set, an EmfPlusBlendFactors object that specifies a blend pattern along a vertical gradient MUST be specified in the OptionalData field of the brush data object.(此标志在EmfPlusLinearEnsementBrushData对象中有意义。如果已设置，则必须在画笔数据对象的OptionalData字段中指定指定沿垂直渐变的混合图案的EmfPlusBlendFactors对象。)

      • FOCUS_SCALES

        static final BitField FOCUS_SCALES
        This flag is meaningful in EmfPlusPathGradientBrushData objects. If set, an EmfPlusFocusScaleData object MUST be specified in the OptionalData field of the brush data object.(此标志在EmfPlusPathJournentBrushData对象中有意义。如果已设置，则必须在画笔数据对象的OptionalData字段中指定EmfPlusFocusScaleData对象。)

      • IS_GAMMA_CORRECTED

        static final BitField IS_GAMMA_CORRECTED
        This flag is meaningful in EmfPlusLinearGradientBrushData, EmfPlusPathGradientBrushData, and EmfPlusTextureBrushData objects. If set, the brush MUST already be gamma corrected; that is, output brightness and intensity have been corrected to match the input image.(此标志在EmfPlusLinearEnsementBrushData、EmfPlusPathEnsementBrushData和EmfPlusTextureBrushData对象中有意义。如果已设置，画笔必须已进行伽玛修正;即，输出亮度和强度已被修正以匹配输入图像。)

      • DO_NOT_TRANSFORM

        static final BitField DO_NOT_TRANSFORM
        This flag is meaningful in EmfPlusTextureBrushData objects. If set, a world space to device space transform SHOULD NOT be applied to the texture brush.(此标志在EmfPlusTextureBrushData对象中有意义。如果设置，世界空间到设备空间的转换不应应用于纹理画笔。)
